      "start_time": 135.41,
      "recording_attendee_id": "883881d1-ab2b-42d6-a382-55beaf95ec07",
      "order_number": 43,
      "text": "Um We'll get you some pricing and then at that point, we can either talk next steps or if it's something that, you know, you're not looking to, to move forward with at the moment, that's ok too."
    },
    {
      "id": "7d29c64b-6e7f-457a-9abe-1877ceee2c31",
      "recording_id": "18fe5e65-3190-42d7-9386-31093d06fa97",
      "end_time": 145.45,
      "start_time": 145.23,
      "recording_attendee_id": "883881d1-ab2b-42d6-a382-55beaf95ec07",
      "order_number": 44,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
