      "recording_attendee_id": "d347dd53-2c29-4ef0-a14a-2dc467ef2216",
      "order_number": 47,
      "text": "Um We have so much going on right now, we have to move our hr department over like I just have so many initiatives going on right now and ruins at capacity."
